{"tid":1136834,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"寶瓶座流星雨約你在『立夏』","createTime":"2019-05-03T09:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T14:23:45.000Z","uid":251778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"644ed51edbd6b574e54add7dd8fcb7362efaf277","tid":1136834,"uid":251778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"寶瓶座&eta;(Eta，讀作〝艾塔〞) 流星雨是每年固定發生的中型流星雨之一，天文台預計將在5月6日至7日間在上空經過的流星雨達到高峰，估計最多每小時可看到40顆左右，加上適逢朔月後，值農曆初三，月相為上弦，不會受月光影響，觀測條件極佳，喜愛觀星的朋友不妨利用週末安排一趟流星之旅。<br />\n<br />\n由於流星雨的輻射點在凌晨兩點左右才升起，所以最適合觀賞的時間在5月7日凌晨。不時劃過夜空的流星，配上明亮的金星、土星、木星和燦爛的夏季銀河，非常值得找個視野遼闊的郊區跟愛人一起觀賞。<br />\n寶瓶座&eta;流星雨是每年4月19日至5月28日出現的中型流星雨，源自哈雷彗星殘餘的塵埃，其特色是流星速度快而明亮。<br />\n如果大家未能把握今次浪漫的流星雨，不防往meteorshowers網站欣賞模擬的天文現象。<a href=\"https://www.meteorshowers.org/view/Eta-Aquariids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meteorshowers.org%2Fview%2FEta-Aquariids&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=484bef7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.meteorshowers.org/view/Eta-Aquariids</a><br />\n有關寶瓶座&eta;流星雨的資料，可以往天文台瀏覽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/gts/event/event-meteor_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fgts%2Fevent%2Fevent-meteor_c.htm&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=daa3dfbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/gts/event/event-meteor_c.htm</a><br />\n#寶瓶座 <br />\nPerry"},{"pid":"8176141cbc3c8a7b598be0489dc6bb60e68434ea","tid":1136834,"uid":206789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"大家會去邊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88421f10d0b6adc106d14d184821cabe74145277","tid":1136834,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"落雨，冇lu"},{"pid":"d9458ee0ed1ecb0b1fdb9a7cb041a39ef332da02","tid":1136834,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"咁多雲 molamola"},{"pid":"f5af4ff5c28c46a6431335d9c8ca71aa0da0e964","tid":1136834,"uid":251778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8176141cbc3c8a7b598be0489dc6bb60e68434ea","tid":1136834,"uid":206789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"大家會去邊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"現在雲開始散。 希望睇到一粒半粒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccqbyKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccqbyKa.jpg&h=ebb6d975&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}